		<a href="http://www.johnhanna.us/TI-nspire.htm">John Hanna's TI Nspire Page</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://ticalc.org">Ticalc.org</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://www.tinspire.com">TI Nspire Official Website</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://www.cemetech.net">Cemetech</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://groups.google.com.au/group/tinspire?hl=en-GB">TI Nspire Google Group</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://www.junemann.nl/maxcoderz/">Maxcoderz</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://www.unitedti.org">United TI</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://www.timath.com">TI Math</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://nelsonsousa.pt">Nelson Sousa's TI Nspire Website</a><br /> 
		<a href="http://handheldgeometry.co.uk">Handheld Geometry</a>
	</div>
</div>
